### Series Parsing

Goodreads encodes series inline: `"The Name of the Wind (The Kingkiller Chronicle, #1)"`. Also handle separate `Series` and `Series Number` columns if present in export.

- Regex on title: `^(.+?)\s*\((.+?),\s*#([\d.]+)\)\s*$`
- Clean title = group 1; series_name = group 2; series_number = group 3 (REAL)
- Upsert into `tbl_book_series`; insert `xref_book_item_series`
- If no match: title as-is, no series record

