## Genre Mapping

Genre tags map to `xref_book_item_genres` (not added as freeform tags). IDs loaded dynamically from DB. Multiple genre tags per book = multiple rows. Tags not matching any map → freeform tag.

There are two mapping structures in the script:

### GENRE_MAP — direct tag → genre

| Tag | Genre | Subgenre |
|---|---|---|
| `fantasy` | Fantasy | — |
| `urban-fantasy` | Fantasy | Urban Fantasy |
| `fairy-tales` | Fantasy | Fairy Tale |
| `magical-realism` | Fantasy | Magical Realism |
| `sci-fi` | Science Fiction | — |
| `romance` | Romance | — |
| `romance-dark` | Romance | Dark |
| `romance-fantasy` | Romance | Fantasy |
| `romance-historical` | Romance | Historical |
| `romance-other` | Romance | — |
| `romance-paranormal` | Romance | Paranormal |
| `romance-scifi` | Romance | Sci-Fi |
| `romance-suspense` | Romance | Romantic Suspense |
| `mystery` | Crime | Mystery |
| `suspense-thriller` | Crime | Suspense/Thriller |
| `gothic` | Horror | Gothic |
| `horror-paranormal` | Horror | Paranormal |
| `contemporary` | Other | Contemporary |
| `historical-fiction` | Other | Historical Fiction |
| `biography` | Biography | — |

### YA_GENRE_SUFFIX_MAP — `ya-{suffix}` tags

`ya-*` tags set `age_level = Young Adult` and map the suffix to a genre. If the suffix is not in this map, it goes to freeform (age level still set).

| Tag | Genre | Subgenre |
|---|---|---|
| `ya-contemporary` | Other | Contemporary |
| `ya-dystopia` | Science Fiction | Dystopian |
| `ya-fantasy` | Fantasy | — |
| `ya-historical` | Other | Historical Fiction |
| `ya-horror` | Horror | — |
| `ya-mystery` | Crime | Mystery |
| `ya-mythology` | Fantasy | Mythology |
| `ya-paranormal` | Horror | Paranormal |
| `ya-romance` | Romance | — |
| `ya-scifi` | Science Fiction | — |
| `ya-suspense` | Crime | Suspense/Thriller |
| `ya-suspense-mystery` | Crime | Mystery *(combined tag; Mystery is alphabetically first)* |

### Freeform only (no genre match in schema)

`queer`, `austen-and-austenesque`, `star-wars`, `tv-movies-video-games`, `kiddie-stuff`, `graphic-novels`, `poly-or-why-choose`, `reference-material`, `not-for-me`, `oz-rules`, `short-stories-or-novellas`, `classics`, `angels-demons`, `giveaway-entry`, `romance-other`, `fantasy-standalone`, `special-edition`, `book-box-or-special-edition`, `litrpg`, and all challenge/tbr/personal tags.

