## Script Interface

```
python migrate_goodreads.py [CSV_PATH] [--db DB_PATH] [--dry-run] [--verbose]
```

- `CSV_PATH` — defaults to `~/Downloads/goodreads_library_export.csv`
- `--db` — defaults to `backend/collectcore.db`
- `--dry-run` — parse only; print full tag inventory with counts + mapping preview; no DB writes
- `--verbose` — print each imported title during full run

### Execution order

1. `python migrate_goodreads.py --dry-run` — review tag inventory
2. Update genre mapping dict in script based on dry-run output
3. `python migrate_goodreads.py` — full import
4. Run verification queries (see below)

